<div class="front">
  <div class="texx">
    <h1 class="head">
      Manage your <br />
      hostel mess <br />
      effortlessly
    </h1>

    <p class="cap">
      Track meals, auto-generate bills, and monitor student registrations — all
      from one dashboard.
    </p>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/Signup" class="btn1">Get started free</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn2">View demo</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rightside">
    <div class="chart-card">
      <div class="chart-top">
        <span>Student registrations · Jan–Dec 2025</span>
        <span class="yoy">+42% YOY</span>
      </div>
      <svg
        viewBox="0 0 340 140"
        preserveAspectRatio="none"
        style="width: 100%; height: 120px; display: block"
      >
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="cg1" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1d9e75" stop-opacity="0.4" />
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1d9e75" stop-opacity="0" />
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
        <path
          d="M0 130 L57 120 L113 105 L170 80 L226 45 L283 15 L340 0 L340 140 L0 140Z"
          fill="url(#cg1)"
        />
        <polyline
          fill="none"
          stroke="#5dcaa5"
          stroke-width="2.5"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          points="0,130 57,120 113,105 170,80 226,45 283,15 340,0"
        />
        <circle cx="340" cy="0" r="4" fill="#5dcaa5" />
      </svg>
      <div class="chart-stats">
        <div><strong>650+</strong><span>Students</span></div>
        <div><strong>18K+</strong><span>Meals served</span></div>
        <div><strong>99.9%</strong><span>Uptime</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="back">
  <div class="graph"><img src="/img/graph.png" class="graph-i" loading="lazy"
  alt="Analytics graph" /></div>

  <div class="right_sidetext">
    <h3 class="head2">Smart Analytics for<br />Better Mess Management</h3>
    <p class="cap2">
      Gain valuable insights into your hostel mess performance with our powerful
      analytics dashboard. Monitor student registrations, track meal consumption
      trends, and generate billing reports automatically. Meal Delight helps
      administrators make faster, smarter decisions with real-time data.
    </p>
    <ul class="features_right">
      <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;Monitor student growth in real time</li>
      <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;Track daily meal usage and trends</li>
      <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;Generate automated billing reports</li>
      <li>&nbsp;&nbsp;Improve mess efficiency and planning</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
